Class Run

  • java.lang.Object
    • eventak.Run

  • public class Run
extends java.lang.Object
    MAIN An application that helps an event organizing agency create and manage events, produce reports, and have contacts. A user(employee) can create an event of any of the following types: - Party: ~ Any private party, held for or by (a) specific person(s). For example: birthdays, weddings, fundraisers. - Conference: ~ Any conference that will have (a) speaker(s) and attendees. This will also implement ticketing of one tier. - Concert: ~ Any show/entertainment event with ticketing of one or more tiers (VIP, regular, etc). A user can also add or browse contacts, which can be connected to venues/etc. They can also create venues, and use them in specific events.
    Version:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    Mariam Maarouf
